Sauron - DNS/DHCP Management System
======


REQUIREMENTS
	- BIND v8 (or newer)
	- DHCP, dhcp v2.0 or newer from ISC  (optional)
	- Perl 5 or better
		- Net::Netmask module
		- Digest::MD5 module
		- Term::ReadKey module
	- PostgresSQL (or add support to your favorite db yourself :)
		- Pg perl module
	- Apache (or any other www-server with CGI support)


TESTED PLATFORMS
	Linux
	Solaris



INSTALLATION
	.... (complete instructions to be added someday :)


	./configure
	make docs
	<read docs... :)>
	<create database (sauron) in postgres>
	cp config.in config
	<edit config>
	make make_tables
	make init_tables
	<run import,import-jyu,contrib/netnames-jyu,... if necessary :)>
	./adduser
	<setup www interface...sauron.cgi>




SUGGESTED READING
	RFC: 952,953,974,1032,1034,1035,1123,1912


